=== Grouping functionality ===
=== Basic grouping ===
123.456789	2	246.913578
234.56789	2	469.13578
456.789012	1	456.789012
=== Grouping with aggregation ===
123.456789	2	246.913578	123.456789	123.456789	123.456789
234.56789	2	469.13578	234.56789	234.56789	234.56789
456.789012	1	456.789012	456.789012	456.789012	456.789012
=== Grouping with HAVING ===
123.456789	2
234.56789	2
=== Grouping with negative values ===
-456.789012	1	-456.789012
-123.456789	2	-246.913578
234.56789	2	469.13578
